## üîë Key Interview Points

‚Ä¢‚Å†  ‚Å†Custom exception *inherits from ‚Å†‚ÄØException‚ÄØ‚Å†*
‚Ä¢‚Å†  ‚Å†‚Å†‚ÄØthrow‚ÄØ‚Å† keyword is used to raise exception
‚Ä¢‚Å†  ‚Å†‚Å†‚ÄØcatch‚ÄØ‚Å† is used to handle it
‚Ä¢‚Å†  ‚Å†Used for *business rule validation*
‚Ä¢‚Å†  ‚Å†Naming convention: ‚Å†‚ÄØException‚ÄØ‚Å† suffix is mandatory

